  "prompt": "My viber on PC doesnt connect to internet. whats the problem? It shows me the messages that other send me but I cant reply through my pc.",
  "response": "There could be several reasons why Viber on your PC isn't connecting to the internet properly. Here is a checklist of common troubleshooting steps that might help resolve the issue:\n\n1. **Internet Connection:**\n   - Ensure your PC is connected to the internet. Test your connection by opening a web browser and navigating to a website.\n   \n2. **Firewall and Antivirus:**\n   - Check if your firewall or antivirus software is blocking Viber. You might need to add Viber to the list of allowed applications.\n\n3. **Viber Service Status:**\n   - Sometimes, Viber\u2019s servers might be down for maintenance or experiencing issues. Check online for any announcements or service status updates from Viber.\n\n4. **App Update:**\n   - Ensure you are using the latest version of Viber on your PC. Updates often include fixes for connectivity issues.\n\n5. **Restart Viber:**\n   - Close Viber completely and relaunch it. This simple step can sometimes resolve connectivity issues.\n\n6. **PC Restart:**\n   - Restart your computer to clear up any temporary issues.\n\n7. **Network Configuration:**\n   - If you're using a proxy or VPN, try disabling them temporarily to see if Viber can connect without them.\n\n8. **Reinstall Viber:**\n   - If other steps don't work, try reinstalling Viber on your PC. This will ensure all settings and files are correctly configured.\n\n9. **Disk Space:**\n   - Ensure your PC has enough free disk space and isn't running out of resources like CPU or RAM.\n\n10. **Viber Linked Devices:**\n    - Sometimes there can be issues with linked devices. Unlink your PC from your Viber account on your phone, then re-link it.\n\n11. **Account Issues:**\n    - Confirm there are no issues with your Viber account, such as being temporarily banned or restricted.\n\nIf you\u2019ve tried all these steps and Viber still isn\u2019t working, you might want to contact Viber Support for further assistance.",
